{"ID":"20220618223200-8lgnh68","Spec":"1","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20220618223200-8lgnh68","title":"word","type":"doc","updated":"20220627102606"},"Children":[{"ID":"20220618223201-xjtfvtt","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20220618223201-xjtfvtt","updated":"20220618223201"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"word","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618223202-yiylpye","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":3,"Properties":{"id":"20220618223202-yiylpye","updated":"20220618223202"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"### ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"如何修改参考文献才能对齐？","Properties":{"id":""}}]},{"ID":"20220618223203-f2acile","Type":"NodeBlockquote","Properties":{"id":"20220618223203-f2acile","updated":"20220618223203"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeBlockquoteMarker","Data":"\u003e ","Properties":{"id":""}},{"ID":"20220618223204-3iyhjv7","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618223204-3iyhjv7","updated":"20220618223204"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"首先[x]后面不要有空格，然后选中所有，两端对齐，悬挂缩进两字符，如果还有没对齐的tab一下就对齐了","Properties":{"id":""}}]}]},{"ID":"20220618223452-pf1x5pq","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220618223452-pf1x5pq"}},{"ID":"20220626152505-f6ggbkh","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220626152505-f6ggbkh","updated":"20220627102606"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"非常感谢您的来信和审稿人对我们的论文《基于强化学习的算力资源度量方法》(稿件编号：202206017)的评论。这些修改意见对修改和完善我们的论文非常有帮助和有价值的，并且对我们的研究具有重要的指导意义。我们尽力对稿件进行了修改，这些修改并不会影响本文的内容和框架。在修回的稿件中，我们用黄色标亮出了修改的部分。我们非常感谢编辑和审稿人的工作并希望修改获得认可。再次非常感谢你们的意见和建议。"}]},{"ID":"20220626152505-mwt6lsd","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220626152505-mwt6lsd"}},{"ID":"20220625162505-o2po0sk","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20220625162505-o2po0sk"}}]}